data.description: **Price Improvement** Looking for country living with ease of access to the city. Look no further this 3 bedroom, 2 bath home has plenty to offer. The spacious living room features high ceilings and fireplace and access to an office area. The primary bedroom with large walk-in closet boasts an ensuite bathroom, ensuring privacy and convenience. The abundance of trees outdoors makes it a peaceful and tranquil area to relax and enjoy barbecues and entertain guests, with plenty of room to store your RV, and boat.
